Usage: _build/macosx64/bin/infinit-drive MODE [OPTIONS...]

Infinit drive management utility:

Modes:
  --create                     Create a drive (a network and volume pair)
  --invite                     Invite a user to join the drive
  --join                       Join a drive you were invited to (Hub operation)
  --export                     Export a drive
  --push                       Push a drive to the Hub
  --fetch                      Fetch drive from the Hub
  --list                       List drives
  --delete                     Delete a drive locally
  --pull                       Remove a drive from the Hub

Miscellaneous:
  -h [ --help ]                Display the help
  -s [ --script ]              Silence all extraneous human friendly messages
  --compatibility-version arg  Force compatibility version
  -v [ --version ]             Display version
  --critical-log               Path to critical log file, none to disable
  -a [ --as ] arg              User to run commands as (default: system user)


